<title>USA: American Rivers has option on Opon stake.</title>
<headline>American Rivers has option on Opon stake.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER, Colo. 1997-06-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>American Rivers Oil Co said Tuesday that it had signed an option to purchase an $8.5 million stake in Opon Development Co from Creston Exploration.</p>
<p>The purchase option followed a May 9 announcement by AROC that Opon had decided not to pursue a previously proposed merger deal struck between the two companies.</p>
<p>Opon's only asset is a 4.55 working interst in a gas field in Colombia, operated by Amoco Corp, American Rivers said.</p>
